   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.760", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr verehrten Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.640", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es soll um Gerechtigkeit gehen,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.720", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber nicht um die gro\u00dfe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.760", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die ganze Welt umfassende, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.040", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von der sehr h\u00e4ufig in diesem Hause die Rede ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.440", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Iustitia fiat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.040", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "pereat mundus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.240", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Erde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.760", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "oder zumindest dieses Land, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.200", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00f6ge ruhig zugrunde gehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.240", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Hauptsache ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.800", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es geschieht der Gerechtigkeit zuliebe."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.000", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es soll um konkrete Gerechtigkeit gehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.560", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die man in Zahlen ausdr\u00fccken kann. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.720", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir stellen uns einen Steuerpflichtigen vor, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.000", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der im Jahr\u00a00 ein zu versteuerndes Einkommen von 40\u00a0000\u00a0Euro hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.000", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In den anschlie\u00dfenden zw\u00f6lf Jahren erh\u00e4lt er j\u00e4hrlich eine Lohnerh\u00f6hung von jeweils 2\u00a0Prozent. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.680", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser Vorgang soll begleitet sein von einer j\u00e4hrlichen Inflationsrate von ebenfalls 2\u00a0Prozent, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.920", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Ideal der EZB, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.160", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was diese Preisstabilit\u00e4t nennt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.000", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Jahr\u00a012 erreicht der Pflichtige, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.320", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie das im Fachjargon hei\u00dft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.840", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann ein Einkommen von gut 50\u00a0000\u00a0Euro. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.160", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ohne dass er sich dessen bewusst ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.520", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat er in der ganzen Zeit keinerlei realen Einkommenszuwachs erzielt; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.040", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn die Inflation hat seine j\u00e4hrlichen nominalen Einkommenszuw\u00e4chse exakt neutralisiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.080", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sein Realeinkommen ist also genauso hoch wie zw\u00f6lf Jahre zuvor; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.240", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenigstens, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.480", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so glaubt er, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.880", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn er die Wirkung der Inflation verstanden hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.320", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "habe er seinen Lebensstandard erhalten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.400", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt kommt die Lohn- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.680", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bzw. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.360", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einkommensteuer ins Spiel. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.800", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie nimmt keinen Bezug auf die unver\u00e4nderte wirtschaftliche Leistungsf\u00e4higkeit des Pflichtigen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.240", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Einkommensteuer tut stattdessen so, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.720", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als h\u00e4tte der gutgl\u00e4ubige Mensch Jahr f\u00fcr Jahr tats\u00e4chliche Lohnzuw\u00e4chse gehabt und w\u00fcrde nunmehr im Jahr\u00a012 ein Einkommen erzielen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.280", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das 25\u00a0Prozent h\u00f6her liege als im Jahr\u00a00. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.520", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die 800 bis 1\u00a0000\u00a0Euro, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.120", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die der Steuerb\u00fcrger j\u00e4hrlich auf dem Papier zus\u00e4tzlich verdiente, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.640", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "behandelt der Steuerfiskus wie reales zus\u00e4tzliches Einkommen und besteuert sie mit etwa 40\u00a0Prozent. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.640", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hei\u00dft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.240", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der arme Mann verliert j\u00e4hrlich etwa 300\u00a0Euro an Kaufkraft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.240", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcber die zw\u00f6lf Jahre also fast 4\u00a0000\u00a0Euro."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.760", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Ganz praktisch. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.520", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kaufkraft ist so unheimlich praktisch; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.920", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich wei\u00df gar nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.080", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob Sie sich das vorstellen k\u00f6nnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.200", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das besonders Ungerechte daran ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.800", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass dieser Effekt nur die Menschen betrifft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.160", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die ein Einkommen bis 53\u00a0000\u00a0Euro erzielen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.080", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn h\u00f6heres Einkommen wird einheitlich linear mit circa 45\u00a0Prozent besteuert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.040", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Population ist nicht betroffen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.720", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dies alles passiert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.760", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ohne dass der Gesetzgeber \u00f6ffentlich sichtbar t\u00e4tig wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.800", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die GroKo schreibt daher, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.880", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diese weitverbreitete Unwissenheit gutgl\u00e4ubiger Menschen ausnutzend, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.960", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in Zeile\u00a02\u00a0437 ihres Vertrages:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.600", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir werden die Steuerbelastung der B\u00fcrger nicht erh\u00f6hen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.601", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie tut dies, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.601", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.640", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "obwohl sich zwischen 2011 und 2016 durch heimliche Steuererh\u00f6hungen die Staatseinnahmen um 33,5\u00a0Milliarden Euro erh\u00f6ht haben und von 2017 bis 2030 um 315\u00a0Milliarden Euro erh\u00f6hen werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.920", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Botschaft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.920", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ohne Steuererh\u00f6hungen die n\u00e4chsten vier Jahre regieren zu wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.160", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist ein Fake."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.680", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Netz m\u00fcsste der \u201eWahrheitsminister\u201c diesen Fake l\u00f6schen lassen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.040", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Koalitionsvertrag steht:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.200", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir halten an der bew\u00e4hrten \u00dcbung fest, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.480", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "alle zwei Jahre einen Bericht zur Entwicklung der kalten Progression vorzulegen und den Einkommensteuertarif im Anschluss entsprechend zu bereinigen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.481", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "H\u00f6rt! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.481", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.482", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "H\u00f6rt! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.482", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.800", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Von dieser \u00dcbung ist bisher nichts bekannt geworden,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.040", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenngleich CDU und FDP seit vielen Jahren dies in ihren Wahlprogrammen versprochen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.280", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber niemals gehalten haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.160", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Wenn Sie am Kinderfreibetrag rumgefummelt haben oder sonst was, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.560", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist das eine v\u00f6llig andere Geschichte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.840", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Sachverst\u00e4ndigenrat zur Begutachtung der gesamtwirtschaftlichen Entwicklung schreibt in seinem Jahresgutachten\u00a02017/2018\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.040", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich zitiere\u00a0\u2013:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.680", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit einer Tarifreform der Einkommensteuer sollten Mehreinnahmen aus der Kalten Progression zur\u00fcckgegeben werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.240", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zumal \u201evor allem die Bezieher mittlerer Einkommen\u201c durch sie belastet werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.480", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Neben diesen heimlichen Steuererh\u00f6hungen durch gesetzgeberische Unterlassung plant die neue Regierung weitere Steuererh\u00f6hungen durch aktive Gesetzes\u00e4nderungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.600", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie will die Abgeltungsteuer auf Zinsertr\u00e4ge abschaffen und damit die ohnehin unwirtschaftlichen Zinserl\u00f6se der Sparer einem individuell h\u00f6heren Steuersatz unterwerfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.601", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Den enteignenden Null- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.601", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.960", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Minizinsen der EZB f\u00fcr alle Formen der Geldanlagen will diese Regierung noch eine zus\u00e4tzlich enteignende Besteuerung hinzuf\u00fcgen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.360", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und dies alles mit der Behauptung: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.160", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir werden keine Mauer bauen, "
